videos.headline: Ramsey finds a wide-open Fryfogle for the TD
videos.description: Indiana's Peyton Ramsey goes up to to a wide-open Ty Fryfogle for the easy 38-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ramsey finds a wide-open Fryfogle for the TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Clifford takes it to the house from 38-yards out
videos.description: Sean Clifford runs right up the middle and finds the end zone from for a 38-yard Penn State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford takes it to the house from 38-yards out) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Brown goes up the middle for the Penn State TD
videos.description: Penn State RB Journey Brown goes right through the Indiana defense for the 35-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown goes up the middle for the Penn State TD) 2019/10/16

videos.headline: Indiana's fake punt goes terribly wrong
videos.description: Indiana tries to run a fake punt, but are unable to convert as Peyton Hendershot is tackled by several Penn State defenders for a loss of four yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Indiana's fake punt goes terribly wrong) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Ramsey cuts into Penn State's lead with a TD
videos.description: Indiana's Peyton Ramsey scores from one yard out, cutting Penn State's lead to three.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ramsey cuts into Penn State's lead with a TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Clifford caps off 9-minute drive with a TD
videos.description: Sean Clifford scores the 1-yard touchdown to cap off an 18-play, nine-minute drive for Penn State.
